- Sretno.
- Hvala gospodine.

237
00:18:55,700 --> 00:18:57,800
- Sretno, Chester.
- Da gospodine.

238
00:18:58,000 --> 00:18:59,800
- Sretno.
- Hvala.

239
00:19:01,400 --> 00:19:02,500
Gospodine.

240
00:19:33,500 --> 00:19:35,700
- Zaustavi ga.
