1161
01:39:41,400 --> 01:39:43,800
Dame i gospodo, pozdravite

1162
01:39:43,800 --> 01:39:47,000
predsjednika Južne Afrike

1163
01:39:47,300 --> 01:39:50,200
 Nelsona Mandelu.

1164
01:40:00,100 --> 01:40:02,600
Nelson Mandela, predsjednik Južne Afrike

1165
01:40:02,700 --> 01:40:05,900
