Ovo se nece svidati All Blacksima.

1167
01:40:10,800 --> 01:40:14,200
Francois, tvoja je zemlja vrlo ponosna na tebe.

1168
01:40:14,900 --> 01:40:15,900
Hvala vam gospodine.

1169
01:40:16,000 --> 01:40:17,800
- Sretno.
- Hvala.

1170
01:40:18,500 --> 01:40:20,900
- Gospodine Predsjednice.
Hvala.

1171
01:40:21,000 --> 01:40:22,700
Neka ti je sa srecom, sine.

1172
01:40:23,700 --> 01:40:25,500
Sretno, sine.

1173
01:40:33,500 --> 01:40:38,600
Chester, želim da znaš da
